Runnable, org.springframework.beans.factory.InitializingBean
public class DbListFilesystemSource
extends FilesystemSource
implements org.springframework.beans.factory.InitializingBean

This is an extension of the filesystem source that reads its list of files to transfer from a database SELECT query. Note that this source currently only supports Spring configuration.
